{
  "stem": "14737.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I went to the consulate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I registered in Prague myself to going to the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Naturally, [INAUDIBLE], that it was almost impossible to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because the quota was so high, I had to wait for years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were many who were registered much before with priorities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But still, I have something at least that maybe some chance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Also, in the meantime, I was seeing what could be there that was could be something to emigrate to go anyplace, if I go maybe to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But to Palestine, as you know from history, there were only certificates given out, about 1,500 a year for the entire world.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was almost impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mean, organizations, some head of them, are going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what's happening now in Brno?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Jewish stores were closed, [? all businesses ?] like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the most important things what happened in Jew-- in Brno was large synagogue, one of the largest, very large, an old one.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in this synagogue was very well-equipped with everything, but a big one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Jews used to come there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was mostly reformed Jews from Prague and Brno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Brno, a lot of very wealthy Jews lived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are mostly manufacturing of textiles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we wake up in the morning, Friday morning, still guards were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they are allowed to go in in this building, only those who belong there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a like a identification who belongs to that building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for those, they allowed, not a stranger, a SS-- in other words, in, in German uniforms.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We hear that this synagogue is burning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We are curious and go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I go to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not far.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
